{"tid":551963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何志平仍熱衷一帶一路, 監獄中教中國營商課程","createTime":"2018-02-06T06:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T06:48:25.000Z","uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e923c30bdcd874cf728d403e233f4381ef908c85","tid":551963,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T06:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E9%80%8F%E9%9C%B2-%E4%BD%95%E5%BF%97%E5%B9%B3%E4%BB%8D%E7%86%B1%E8%A1%B7%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF-%E7%8D%84%E4%B8%AD%E6%95%99%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%87%9F%E5%95%86%E8%AA%B2%E7%A8%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E9%2580%258F%25E9%259C%25B2-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E4%25BB%258D%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A1%25B7%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E7%258D%2584%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2587%259F%25E5%2595%2586%25E8%25AA%25B2%25E7%25A8%258B%2F&d=hIPhOiaFzJJfBAMIi8cg%2BROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=35a0e43e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E9%2580%258F%25E9%259C%25B2-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E4%25BB%258D%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A1%25B7%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E7%258D%2584%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2587%259F%25E5%2595%2586%25E8%25AA%25B2%25E7%25A8%258B%2F&h=6df62557\" target=\"_blank\">http://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E9%80%8F%E9%9C%B2-%E4%BD%95%E5%BF%97%E5%B9%B3%E4%BB%8D%E7%86%B1%E8%A1%B7%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF-%E7%8D%84%E4%B8%AD%E6%95%99%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%87%9F%E5%95%86%E8%AA%B2%E7%A8%8B/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n【保釋被拒】辯方透露：何志平仍熱衷一帶一路　獄中教中國營商課程<br />\n2018/2/6 &mdash; 12:17<br />\n<br />\n民政事務局前局長何志平涉代表中國一間能源公司向非洲高官賄賂，早前在美國被起訴，何志平今日在香港時間凌晨出庭應訊，惟法官再拒絕何保釋申請。《蘋果日報》引述辯方律師在庭上指出，還柙在紐約大都會懲教中心的何志平仍熱衷於「一帶一路」，主動在懲教中心教授與中國做生意技巧、擔任GED（普通教育發展證書）導師等。<br />\n<br />\nGED課程屬於普通教育發展證書考試（General Educational Development），為美國的高中試。據《明報》報道，何志平在懲教中心教授有關「一帶一路」及於中國創業的課程。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，控方律師Daniel Richenthal表示，何志平被拘捕後，在獄中與總部位於上海的中國能源公司高層保持頻繁通訊。<br />\n<br />\n負責案件的法官Forrest認同辯方指出，何志平在全球有知名度，工作性質依賴個人信譽。不過，她引述控方文件指，有中國官媒在事件被揭發後，以「政治檢控」為由評價起訴動機，故法官不認同何志平一旦潛逃，其國際形象將完全被毀的保釋理據，認為如果何志平逃到香港，則可能不會感到尷尬。"},{"pid":"73555a28fd6eb965cfef234a305d3593be450fef","tid":551963,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T06:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4728c40785df2464d4fa038e0254923d8d86b9","tid":551963,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T06:19:21.000Z","msg":"Cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f967ed61aad6e9d1af134ce2bf8120bab7916c40","tid":551963,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T06:19:43.000Z","msg":"教人賄賂大陸d官？"},{"pid":"4f14eae79d917d77c3f972008abf202046758c9f","tid":551963,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T06:20:05.000Z","msg":"有中國官媒在事件被揭發後，以「政治檢控」為由評價起訴動機，故法官不認同何志平一旦潛逃，其國際形象將完全被毀的保釋理據，認為如果何志平逃到香港，則可能不會感到尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/